description: Welcome to this luxurious 2-bedroom apartment with stunning city views and high-end finishes throughout. This premium unit features stainless steel appliances, marble countertops, and hardwood floors. Building amenities include 24/7 concierge service, valet parking, rooftop pool with city views, fitness center, and private dining room. Perfect for professionals seeking luxury living in the heart of Boyle Heights.

Elegant 3-bedroom townhouse featuring custom marble countertops, premium hardwood floors, and a private garden with outdoor dining area. This sophisticated home offers an open-concept kitchen with Viking appliances, formal dining room, and spacious living area with fireplace. Walking distance to world-class shopping and fine dining establishments. Includes 2-car garage and security system.

Features include in-unit laundry, custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, and floor-to-ceiling windows with city views. Building amenities include fitness center, spa, rooftop deck, and 24/7 security. Perfect for professionals seeking a maintenance-free lifestyle in a prestigious location.

Master suite includes walk-in closet and spa-like bathroom with dual vanities. Private backyard with pool, spa, and outdoor kitchen. Located in prestigious neighborhood with 24/7 security and gated access.
